---
// The Longer Arc — subtle Phase 2 hint
---

<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">

    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
      <span class="w-6 h-px bg-[var(--border-medium)]"></span>
      <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase tracking-[3px]">A longer arc</span>
      <span class="w-6 h-px bg-[var(--border-medium)]"></span>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="text-base sm:text-lg font-mono text-[var(--text-primary)] leading-relaxed mb-6">
      "Corporations built empires on structured data about you.<br/>
      <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We're giving you the same thing &mdash; and making it portable enough to leave the planet.</span>"
    </blockquote>

    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] italic">
      Phase 1 is your personal agent. The standard underneath was designed to travel.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
